{"tid":2109702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：共產黨像「眾星捧月」總攬全局　協調領導","createTime":"2020-07-15T11:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T02:12:44.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"601dd23dd209b1d44ba5f48e005448914507b195","tid":2109702,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">是我們心中的<span class=\"red\">紅月亮</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GDL5YEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGDL5YEi.png&h=039757bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記、國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平，在內地新一期《求是》雜誌發表文章。文章表示，中國特色社會主義最本質的特徵是中國共產黨領導，<strong>黨是最高政治領導力量，黨是領導一切</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，堅持黨的領導，首先是堅持黨中央權威和集中統一領導，這是黨的領導的最高原則，任何時候任何情況下都不能含糊、不能動搖，必須增強政治意識、大局意識、核心意識、看齊意識，自覺維護黨中央權威和集中統一領導，自覺在思想上政治上行動上，同黨中央保持高度一致。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，中國社會主義政治制度優越性的一個突出特點，是黨總攬全局、協調各方的領導核心作用，<strong>形象地說是「眾星捧月」，「月」的意思就是中國共產黨</strong>，中國最大的國情就是中國共產黨的領導。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537950-20200715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537950-20200715.htm&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1513742e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537950-20200715.htm&h=01697fa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537950-20200715.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fcc1998ff1614e5634f246cae7561f8d0efdd30d","tid":2109702,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">坦白講，我覺得以前的國歌更能夠體現習主席的宏願和理想：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q74yKaeTqB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ74yKaeTqB0&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=67b0c013\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q74yKaeTqB0</a>"},{"pid":"1c0ca59fb5a1b4a57e8438bee76c6b683da57863","tid":2109702,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"咁太陽呢"},{"pid":"b20da16db2753adbe89d360f8a84cd4546c4b8bc","tid":2109702,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/3cf2827c6a7eaa446d45055c2d3579ce443b8a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2F3cf2827c6a7eaa446d45055c2d3579ce443b8a12.jpg&h=23be5e3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c3afb422e2a6fa4eb9c2bd8d1408c311dddc828","tid":2109702,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"七星伴月<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820d937c87eb96398c4c94da967f0a3954bafc1f","tid":2109702,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601dd23dd209b1d44ba5f48e005448914507b195","tid":2109702,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">是我們心中的<span class=\"red\">紅月亮</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GDL5YEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGDL5YEi.png&h=039757bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記、國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平，在內地新一期《求是》雜誌發表文章。文章表示，中國特色社會主義最本質的特徵是中國共產黨領導，<strong>黨是最高政治領導力量，黨是領導一切</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，堅持黨的領導，首先是堅持黨中央權威和集中統一領導，這是黨的領導的最高原則，任何時候任何情況下都不能含糊、不能動搖，必須增強政治意識、大局意識、核心意識、看齊意識，自覺維護黨中央權威和集中統一領導，自覺在思想上政治上行動上，同黨中央保持高度一致。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，中國社會主義政治制度優越性的一個突出特點，是黨總攬全局、協調各方的領導核心作用，<strong>形象地說是「眾星捧月」，「月」的意思就是中國共產黨</strong>，中國最大的國情就是中國共產黨的領導。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537950-20200715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https: